{
 "file": "_STGX7.bin",
 "source_size": 27148,
 "built_size": 29154,
 "edits": [
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1083",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……你在那儿吧、西格·韦德纳？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b8ef29e7b7eb7ce7d002e7f8e824ef4bebaee82ce88205000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x10ba",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……亏你能找到这里",
   "zh_hex": "150909eab7e7b8e7c6e9d2e7d7e7b9ef31000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x10ef",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是从NT研那帮人嘴里问出来的",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6e88aeed3eed6ea0ce7b7e910efb2eae2ef31e997efbeefcfe7b400000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1102",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这里、就是那个叫艾因的男人死去的地方{00}吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9ef3102e7c5e7b6e7b7e828e8c1e8d6ef33e7b4ea95efb2ef6ae7ebe7b4ef63efb100e7d0050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x114e",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……嗯",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8650000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1170",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "也是你亲手了结瑟拉的地方……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c0e7b6e7b8e894ef66e7bae868e8aae7c2e7b4ef63efb109090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1189",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……还是另一个我死去的地方",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7f7e7b6e99befb6e828efccef6ae7ebe7b4ef63efb100000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x11b6",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "…………",
   "zh_hex": "150909090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x11da",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "想不起也难怪、关于过去的记忆、我打从{00}一开始就没有",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e6e7b5e847e7c0e866ea0702e8bbe879ef36e7ebe7b4e996eac602efcce7f5e88a00efb6e7fae908e7c5e7d8e7cb00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1200",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是那个曾被称作瑟蕾因·伊克斯贝利的{00}女人的克隆体……",
   "zh_hex": "158be7b6e7b7e828ea2ae7f1ea01ef2fe8aae84cef3304e969e7d5e7c8e857e82ee7b400b0b4e7b4e7d5ed16bc09090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x121b",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那就是我、没错吧、西格·韦德纳？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7c5e7b6efcc02e7d8e885e7d002e7f8e824ef4bebaee82ce88205000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1250",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……老实说、我并不希望你察觉到这一点",
   "zh_hex": "150909e9cae87fe7ed02efcce957e7b5e87be965e7b8ea8be8aee7d7e7b9efb6e8220000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1264",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "作为瑟拉的备份而被造出来的你、",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2fe7c1e8aae7c2e7b4e877ea22e89ce7f1e93eefbeefcfe7b4e7b802000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x127b",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "如今、是唯一一个能启动那套系统的存在",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f0efb902e7b6ea89efb6efb6e828e7c6ea3bef30e7b7eb30e941e929e7b4e993ef29000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12b5",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我真有那种力量？",
   "zh_hex": "158be820e7cbe7b7e7d1dae8510500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12e2",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……应该有、毕竟造出你的人可是艾因",
   "zh_hex": "150909e873e898e7cb02ea2cef2ce93eefbee7b8e7b4efb2e7c4e7b6e8d6ef33000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1316",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "艾因·雷维……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d6ef3304e8afea54090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x133b",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你正是由身处塞壬计划中枢的那个男人、{00}亲手造出来的存在……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8ef3be7b6e8a6e88de903e950ec59ea55ea74ef4eec75e7b4e7b7e828ea95efb20200e894ef66e93eefbeefcfe7b4e993ef2909090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1360",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你并非单纯的工具、而是作为那男人的理{00}想而诞生的",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e957e8f0e918eb66e7b4eae4ea1402e89ce7b6ef2fe7c1e7b7ea95efb2e7b4e87200e7e6e89ced06ef8de7b400000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x139a",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可他已经是个死人了、连我、也只知道他{00}的名字",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e80cef3ae8b7e7b6e828a7b4e7ba02e86e8b02e7c0ef32e85ae82ae80c00e7b4e8ace980000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13d5",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不……那男人定下的计划、如今仍在持续{00}运转",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b50909e7b7ea95efb2e867ef4de7b4ea55ea7402e7f0efb9eab9ef29e9efe9ad00e986e9c2000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13f6",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你的觉醒、还有泰拉·斯欧诺的{00}再度现身、就是最好的证据",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b4e8aeeb2002e7f7e7cbeaeae7c204e7c8eb91e972e7b400e80be96de82fe88d02e7c5e7b6e8c5e7c7e7b4eba3e8cc000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1430",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你太高估我了吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e86ae812ed1fefcce7bae7d00500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1441",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "无论是我、还是那个叫艾因的男人、都没{00}有那么大的力量",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dce8dce7b68b02e7f7e7b6e7b7e828e8c1e8d6ef33e7b4ea95b402e840e7d800e7cbe7b7e7bdbee7b4dae85100000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1477",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "瑟拉曾被艾因操控……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8aae7c2ea2ae7f1e8d6ef33eac7ea3f09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1488",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怀着连累众多人丧命的悔恨、就此消逝了",
   "zh_hex": "15eb03e86de86eec33eafbe7e9efb2efdce853e7b4eb86e9be02e7c5e7cae928ec9de7ba00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14a6",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我不打算让同样的悲剧重演",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b5e7f5e889e7f9e85de7dae7b4e9dfecb5e8a1ea2f000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14d3",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你无论如何、都要和我一战吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7dce8dce7f0efbc02e840ef2ae7d3efccefb6ef28e802050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14ff",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我曾向她发誓、绝不让任何人{00}利用瑟拉的力量作恶",
   "zh_hex": "158bea2a9de88ee870eff002e91ce7b5e7f9e89a8ab400e82ed8e8aae7c2e7b4dae851ef2fe7de00000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x151c",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "如今、这个约定……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f0efb902e7b9e828e9ace86709090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x154c",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就让我来兑现吧！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e7f9efccefcfeddee82fe7d0ef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x157f",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……干劲十足嘛",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8d3eb50ea4aea1ee936000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x158d",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你既然有这个心、那也好、想说的话、就{00}先搁到后头",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e8c4e7efe7cbe7b9e828e82d02e7b7e7c0e7c702e7e6e7ede7b4e81f02e7c500ef8bed6ae7d7e7fee92e00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15af",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、做好相应的觉悟、再放马过来吧！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602e81ce7c7e8b1e873e7b4e8aeea1902e80be86ce84fef36efcfe7d0ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15f0",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔、被反将一军了吗……真难看",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d02e7f1e87ce84a87e7e0e7bae8020909e820e866e7f600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1631",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你知道、我为何特意{00}大老远赶到这里来吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e85ae82a028be7c18ae7cfef3c00bee9cae94cea04e7d7e7b9ef31d9e802060500000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1665",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不就是来做个了断的吗！{00}还能有别的什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e7c5e7b6d9e81ce828e7bae982e7b4e8020600e7f7e7c6e7cbe7e5e7b4e7dde7bd06050000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x169a",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔、你这个笨蛋……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d02e7b8e7b9e828eb12ea6d0909ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16cd",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我特意亲自前来、就是为了给你……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7cfef3ce894efb5ef51efcf02e7c5e7b6e7c1e7bae839e7b809090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16ed",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "狠狠地来上一拳！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ec7aec7aef63efcfef4cefb6ea65ef97ef970000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1730",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1765",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1793",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "给我清醒一点、西格·韦德纳！",
   "zh_hex": "15e839efcce995eb20efb6e82202e7f8e824ef4bebaee82ce882ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17c4",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bd0909ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17e8",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "再说了、什么不让人拿力量作恶、别一个{00}人擅自做决定！",
   "zh_hex": "15e80be7ede7ba02e7dde7bde7b5e7f9b4e9a7dae851ef2fe7de02e7e587e82800b4eb5dabe81ce8abe867060000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1806",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你从一开始、{00}就完全无视了我的意志吧！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e88a87e7fae9080200e7c5e87ebbe7dce9d9e7ba8be7b4ef3cea18e7d00605000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x183e",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔、可是你……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d02e7c4e7b6e7b809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1865",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "小看我、也要有个限度！",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ee7f6efcc02e7c0ef2ae7cbe828eb23e96def970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x187d",
   "jp_len": 40,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你以为我是那种、会被一个死人摆布的软{00}弱之人吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7f3e7c1efcce7b6e7b7e7d102e7e2e7f1efb6e828ef6aefb2eb8be831e7b4eb4700e9d1e7cdefb2e802ef9705000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18a5",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就算求我、我也绝不会那么做！我要按自{00}己想活的方式去活！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e889e93aefcc02efcce7c0e91ce7b5e7e2e7b7e7bde81cef97efccef2aea76efb500e8c9e7e6e8d4e7b4efb1ea26e7ebe8d4ef970000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18ef",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "…………",
   "zh_hex": "150909090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18f8",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "她……瑟拉看似强势、内心却一直害怕自{00}己的软弱",
   "zh_hex": "15e88e0909e8aae7c2e7f6e944e8ade8fd02e99ae82deadfefb6e875e988e958efb500e8c9e7b4eb47e9d1000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x191f",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "她说、因为自己一无所有、只能靠逞强来{00}保护自己……",
   "zh_hex": "15e88ee7ed02ef33e7c1efb5e8c9efb6e7dce7fbe7cb02ef32e7c6e8c7e9ebe8adefcf00ea47e8e0efb5e8c909090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1942",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……她曾这么说过、但你、似乎和她不一{00}样",
   "zh_hex": "150909e88eea2ae7b9e7bde7edef3602e7dbe7b802e944e933e7d3e88ee7b5efb600e7da0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x197a",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我说不定也是一样的哦？",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7ede7b5e867e7c0e7b6efb6e7dae7b4e9190500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1989",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "老实说、对于自己的真实身份、我其实相{00}当动摇",
   "zh_hex": "15e9cae87fe7ed02e7bee879efb5e8c9e7b4e820e87fe88dea2202efcce8cfe87fe8b100ef53ef30ebcc0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19a8",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我来找你打、有一半、其实也算是迁怒罢{00}了",
   "zh_hex": "15efccefcfe9d2e7b8e7f502e7cbefb6eade02e8cfe87fe7c0e889e7b6eeb3ee1eeaef00e7ba0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19e1",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "能这样毫不掩饰地断言、这正是你的坚强{00}吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c6e7b9e7daea0ae7b5ec72eec8ef63e982efd702e7b9ef3be7b6e7b8e7b4eb80e8ad00e7d00000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a06",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你确实……或许正是艾因理想中的存在",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e88ce87f0909e905e8a7ef3be7b6e8d6ef33e872e7e6ef4ee7b4e993ef2900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a3e",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "喂……你又来刚才那一套了？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bd0909e7b8e8f1efcfe8bce836e7b7efb6eb30e7ba05000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a6e",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不……不是的",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b50909e7b5e7b6e7b40000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a7b",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不被过去和自身的处境压垮、只是自由而{00}坚强地活着……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e7f1ef36e7ebe7d3efb5e88de7b4e903eb81e992ed4302ef32e7b6efb5e8a6e89c00eb80e8adef63e8d4e86d090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a9e",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "从这层意义上说、你或许正是他的理想",
   "zh_hex": "15e88ae7b9ebc1ef3ce8ceef4ce7ed02e7b8e905e8a7ef3be7b6e80ce7b4e872e7e600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ab9",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我只是这么觉得罢了",
   "zh_hex": "150909efccef32e7b6e7b9e7bde8aee80aeaefe7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ae4",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "若真是如此、那或许多亏了和我并肩作战{00}的伙伴们",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e7e820e7b6e7f0e7ca02e7b7e905e8a7e7e9eab7e7bae7d3efcce957eb16ef2fef2800e7b4e7fdea72e7bb000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b02",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么生体CPU、什么强化人、明明背负{00}着那么沉重的身世……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bdef8def4feed0eed4e02b02e7dde7bde8ade9a5efb202ef39ef39e9e4e92c00e86de7b7e7bde983e8a1e7b4e88de83c0909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b24",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我身边、却尽是些坚强地活着的家伙",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce88de89902eadfe8f2e7b6e8a4eb80e8adef63e8d4e86de7b4e7dfe7fd000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b44",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "想必、我也被他们感化了吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e6e86002efcce7c0e7f1e80ce7bbe87de9a5e7bae7d0000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b70",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "…………",
   "zh_hex": "150909090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b79",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "至今为止的事、请容我重新道歉、{00}对不起、瑟蕾因",
   "zh_hex": "15e897a2e7c1e869e7b4a902e83aed2f8be8a1ef8ae82ae9270200e7bee7b5e84702e8aae84cef3300000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b95",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是我小看你了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6efcce83ee7f6e7b8e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1bc5",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嘛、懂就好",
   "zh_hex": "15e93602e8b0e7c5e7c70000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1bf6",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……瑟蕾因？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8aae84cef33050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c19",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我要回到伙伴们那里去",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef2aef52e7d7e7fdea72e7bbe7b7ef31e7eb00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c25",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "和你这一战、白白浪费了不少时间",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d3e7b8e7b9efb6ef2802e809e809ed81e95de7bae7b5efacef2de8fc000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c40",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "得快点回去……",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ae85fe822ef52e7eb09090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c77",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那、我也一起去吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b702efcce7c0efb6e847e7ebe7d0000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ca0",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……你也去？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b8e7c0e7eb05000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cc4",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我想亲眼见证、你究竟能走到哪一步",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7e6e894e90be85ceba302e7b8e906ef2ce7c6e890e7d7e8ffefb6ea93000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cf7",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "也是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c0e7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d39",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那可不行",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7c4e7b5efd600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d6e",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你们这么轻易就言归于好、可让人头疼",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7bbe7b9e7bde990e964e7c5efd7e947e879e7c702e7c4e7f9efb2e92eecf10000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1daa",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……什么人！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7dde7bdefb2ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1dcf",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……军团、与您同样、{00}是被造出来的存在……",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7e0ea5e02e832e835e85de7da0200e7b6e7f1e93eafd9e7b4e993ef2909090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e01",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "和我一样？你这家伙、在说什么……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d3efccefb6e7da05e7b8e7b9e7dfe7fd02ef29e7ede7dde7bd09090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e31",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……塞壬系统",
   "zh_hex": "150909e950ec59e941e929000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e6d",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e98",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "旧吉翁军为对抗联邦、而推进开发的心理{00}兵器……",
   "zh_hex": "15eac8e7d9ee88e7e0e7c1e7bee912ef2ed102e89ceaabe892e7fae870e7b4e82de87200cee8c3090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1eba",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "而为那套系统所造的、正是瑟蕾因·伊克{00}斯贝利……",
   "zh_hex": "15e89ce7c1e7b7eb30e941e929e7fbe93ee7b402ef3be7b6e8aae84cef3304e969e7d500e7c8e857e82e090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ed4",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那不正是您吗？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7b5ef3be7b6e835e80205000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f04",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "难道、是你吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e866e82a02e7b6e7b8e8020605000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f35",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "西格？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f8e824050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f56",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……本应被封存的你、原本是不该苏醒过{00}来的",
   "zh_hex": "150909efa6e873e7f1eb83e993e7b4e7b802e8e4efa6e7b6e7b5e898ec8deb20ef3600efcfe7b4000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f79",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可是瑟蕾因、你已经觉醒了、{00}既然如此……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b6e8aae84cef3302e7b8ef3ae8b7e8aeeb20e7ba0200e8c4e7efe7f0e7ca0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1faf",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是叫霍利博士吧？……莱比锡研究所的负{00}责人",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e8c1ebfee82eec4da5e7d0050909e846e825ee8aea0ce906e7fbe7b4e92c00eba6b40000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fcb",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "因为他原本也是弗拉纳冈机关的研究员",
   "zh_hex": "15ef33e7c1e80ce8e4efa6e7c0e7b6e9b5e7c2e882eb7ee7e4e8bbe7b4ea0ce906e84900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ff9",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、把我唤醒的、是你？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e81befccec0eeb20e7b402e7b6e7b80500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2025",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您和塞壬系统……就这么放着不用、实在{00}太可惜了",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e7d3e950ec59e941e9290909e7c5e7b9e7bde86ce86de7b5efb302e87fef2900e86ae7c4e9c8e7ba00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2041",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……来、跟我走吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcf02e973efcce890e7d0000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2052",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您那份力量、本就不该为了人类而施展",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e7b7ea22dae85102d2e7c5e7b5e898e7c1e7bab4e841e89ceb8de98900000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2090",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "…………",
   "zh_hex": "150909090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20b4",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……瑟拉？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8aae7c2050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20e1",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你似乎、把我错当成了什么便利的工具",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e944e93302e81b8be885c4e837e7bae7dde7bde8fae82ee7b4eae4ea1400000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20fb",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我就是我！自己的归宿、由我自己决定！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7c5e7b6efccef97efb5e8c9e7b4e947ec1102e8a6efccefb5e8c9e8abe867ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x212c",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "…………",
   "zh_hex": "150909090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2135",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……容我更正、看来您并不只是个工具",
   "zh_hex": "150909ed2f8be952ef3b02e7f6d9e835e957e7b5ef32e7b6e828eae4ea1400000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2150",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您啊……还真是个难以驾驭的工具",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e7c30909e7f7e820e7b6e828e866e7f3e953edcae7b4eae4ea1400000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2162",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所以、回收时用上些粗暴的手段、也是迫{00}不得已了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fbe7f302ef52e926ef2defb3ef4ce8a4ebe5ea4fe7b4ef66ea6b02e7c0e7b6eb7000e7b5e80aef3ae7ba00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21a9",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……瑟蕾因、小心！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8aae84cef3302e83ee82def970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21cc",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看来不打倒那个碍事的家伙、就回不了主{00}天使号了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6efcfe7b5e7f5e848e7b7e828e8c6efb8e7b4e7dfe7fd02e7c5ef52e7b5e7bae95400e844e83fe833e7ba0909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21e9",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "西格……抱歉、能帮我一把吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f8e8240909e922e92702e7c6e910efccefb6e81be80205000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x221f",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我说过了、要亲眼见证你能走到哪一步！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7edef36e7ba02ef2ae894e90be85ceba3e7b8e7c6e890e7d7e8ffefb6ea93ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2260",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "太好了！那么、动手吧、西格！",
   "zh_hex": "15e86ae7c7e7baef97e7b7e7bd02ef30ef66e7d002e7f8e824ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2293",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……好！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c7ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22c0",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊……拉、乌……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c30909e7c202e94d0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22d6",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……对、对不起……",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7be02e7bee7b5e8470909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2313",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那个少女……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e828efacefad09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x233d",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "她刚才在呼唤某人的名字、看来背后另有{00}人在操纵吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e88ee8bce836ef29ea3cec0eeae8b4e7b4e8ace98002e7f6d9e9e4e7fee99be7cb00b4ef29eac7e8e6e7d0000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2384",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "…………",
   "zh_hex": "150909090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x238d",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "担心去PLANT的娜塔尔舰长她们……",
   "zh_hex": "15e9fde82de7ebeed4e024ea9ceed3eed6e7b4e7eae945e7e1e7d4ef34e88ee7bb0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23a5",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "赶快、和主天使号会合吧",
   "zh_hex": "15ea04e85f02e7d3e954e844e83fe833e7e2efc0e7d000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23d6",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……嗯",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8650000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2402",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "住手啊、西格！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e859ef66e7c302e7f8e824ef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x240d",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你居然和瑟拉打了起来……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8ea4ce7efe7d3e8aae7c2e7f5e7bae847efcf0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2442",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……咦咦！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef49ef49ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2473",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你们俩、怎么会在一起！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7bbeb7b02e7f2e7bde7e2ef29efb6e847ef970500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24a8",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嘛、算是误会解开了吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e93602e889e7b6ea33e7e2e89de7fae7bae7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24bc",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽然要说服这个死脑筋、可费了我好大的{00}劲",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8e7efef2ae7ede9f1e7b9e828a7eb67ef5602e7c4e95de7ba8be7c7bee7b400eb50000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24f3",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那也叫说服？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7c0e8c1e7ede9f1050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2522",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "细节就算了",
   "zh_hex": "15eb9aebece7c5e889e7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2530",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "比起这个……",
   "zh_hex": "15e825e847e7b9e8280909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x255f",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你是蜜安·法琳吧、我在研究所的资料里{00}见过你",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b6e98ee7fcef4be84ee9a9e7d002efccef29ea0ce906e7fbe7b4eba7eb8cef3100e85cef36e7b800000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2597",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嗯、嗯……",
   "zh_hex": "15e86502e86509090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25bb",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "能在这里相遇也是缘分、就顺便借你一把{00}力吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c6ef29e7b9ef31e8b1ea43e7c0e7b6ecf9efae02e7c5eab4e8faeadce7b8efb6e81b00efb0e7d0000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25f4",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……咦？",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef4905000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25fb",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "西、西格……这到底是个什么情况啊？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f802e7f8e8240909e7b9e7d7e9b4e7b6e828e7dde7bde88be8d0e7c30500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x262a",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我也有点摸不着头脑",
   "zh_hex": "1509098be7c0e7cbe822ed7ae7b5e86de92eeb670000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2638",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、关于瑟蕾因的事、我已经知道、用{00}不着再担心了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602e8bbe879e8aae84cef33e7b4a9028bef3ae8b7e85ae82a02d800e7b5e86de80be9fde82de7ba0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2671",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么嘛……我急急忙忙赶来阻止、感觉亏{00}大了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bde9360909efccea62ea62ea06ea06ea04efcfe8efe86902e87de8aeeab700efa5e7ba000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x268d",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、太好了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602e86ae7c7e7ba090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x269a",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "因为我一直觉得、西格和瑟拉自相残杀、{00}绝对是不对的",
   "zh_hex": "15ef33e7c1efccefb6e875e8aee80a02e7f8e824e7d3e8aae7c2efb5e8b1e97be89b0200e91ce7bee7b6e7b5e7bee7b40000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26d7",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "但与此同时……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dbe832e7cae85def2d09090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26e5",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们也查明、这场战争的背后、似乎藏着{00}某个我们不知道的人",
   "zh_hex": "158be7bbe7c0eae9ef3902e7b9e876ef28e852e7b4e9e4e7fe02e944e933ed03e86d00eae8e8288be7bbe7b5e85ae82ae7b4b4000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2725",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那家伙……不、是那些家伙？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7dfe7fd0909e7b502e7b6e7b7e8a4e7dfe7fd050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2734",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "总之那些家伙、想利用这场战争本身来谋{00}划什么、",
   "zh_hex": "15e881e7cde7b7e8a4e7dfe7fd02e7e6e82ed8e7b9e876ef28e852d2e88dd9ea6e00ea74e7dde7bd0200000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2752",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我的伙伴们、此刻正赶往扎夫特与联邦军{00}决战的战场",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b4e7fdea72e7bb02e7cae91fef3bea04e911e84be830e7cfe832ef2eefaae7e000e8abef28e7b4ef28e87600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2774",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所以、蜜安·法琳、希望你也能搭把手",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fbe7f302e98ee7fcef4be84ee9a902e87be965e7b8e7c0e7c6eb09e81bef660000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2791",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为了守护我的伙伴",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1e7bae8a8e8e0efcce7b4e7fdea72000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27cb",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这样啊……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7dae7c30909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27d3",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽说我个人对西格、还有好多话想说……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8e7edefcce828efb2e7bee7f8e82402e7f7e7cbe7c7e7e9e81fe7e6e7ed09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27f7",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嗯、好啊、我帮忙",
   "zh_hex": "15e86502e7c7e7c302efcce910ea0600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2829",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "既然是这种事、那就不能不管了呢",
   "zh_hex": "15e8c4e7efe7b6e7b9e7d1efb802e7b7e7c5e7b5e7c6e7b5e93be7bae90700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2858",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、协定成立",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e8f6e867e837e86b000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2869",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "快、出发吧、前往PLANT",
   "zh_hex": "15e85f02afe870e7d002bae911eed4e024ea9ceed3eed60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2886",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "同一时刻",
   "zh_hex": "15e85defb6ef2de91f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2891",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "PLANT周边",
   "zh_hex": "15eed4e024ea9ceed3eed6ea5ce8990000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28f1",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "即将抵达会合点",
   "zh_hex": "15e855e84ae96eef2be7e2efc0e82200000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x291f",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "…………",
   "zh_hex": "150909090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2943",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他们会来吗？奥古和大天使号的诸位……",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ce7bbe7e2efcfe80205e82be84de7d3efa5e844e83fe833e7b4ea56e834090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2978",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……他们一定会来",
   "zh_hex": "150909e80ce7bbefb6e867e7e2efcf00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2982",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "因为想要阻止这场战争的心愿、他们也是{00}一样的",
   "zh_hex": "15ef33e7c1e7e6ef2ae8efe869e7b9e876ef28e852e7b4e82de96102e80ce7bbe7c0e7b600efb6e7dae7b400000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29a9",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "（说得是啊……拉米亚斯舰长）",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8ee7ede80ae7b6e7c30909e7c2e878e7d6e7c8e7d4ef34ef8f000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5c32",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一路辛苦了",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6e8d2ea58e9e6e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5c3f",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "感谢你将这条『宇宙世纪路线』、一直玩{00}到了最后",
   "zh_hex": "15e87de8b2e7b8e84ae7b9e9d40ce8bee8bfe83ceb99e8d2e9160d02efb6e875e97000e7d7e7bae8c5e7fe00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5c5f",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "另外、隆德·贝尔队的战斗、就先在此暂{00}告一段落……",
   "zh_hex": "15e99be8f702ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e7b4ef28e7ff02e7c5ef8bef29e7cae9ff00e8e5efb6ea6be92a090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5c7e",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过游戏本身仍可继续、今后也请你尽情{00}享受",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef36ea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02efb9e7fee7c0e83ae7b8e8f2e88b00ec06e8c80000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5ca3",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "此外、为通关本路线的你、还特意准备了{00}特别关卡",
   "zh_hex": "15e7cae8f702e7c1ef59e8bbefa6e8d2e916e7b4e7b802e7f7e7cfef3ce87ae877e7ba00e7cfe7e5e8bbe80100000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5cca",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是与另行奋战至今的大天使队进行的特{00}别演习",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e832e99befd6ef46ef28e897efb9e7b4efa5e844e83fe7c9e892efd6e7b4e7cf00e7e5ea2feab6000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5ceb",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "与他们一战、检验一下你亲手培养的部队{00}实力、也不失为乐事",
   "zh_hex": "15e832e80ce7bbefb6ef2802ee40ea99efb6ef4de7b8e894ef66edfeec0be7b4ef70e7c900e87fefb002e7c0e7b5e8a5e7c1ec04efb800000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5d10",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特殊演习』、便可与{00}他们一战",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29abe8a6e7beef28c0e966eaaa0ce7cfed7bea2feab60d02e8fae7c4e83200e80ce7bb87ef28000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5d35",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、『SD高达G世代DS』",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd020cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83ce8e7ef96ef9e0d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5d59",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后也请你慢慢享受、直到最后",
   "zh_hex": "15efb9e7fee7c0e83ae7b8e979e979ec06e8c802e875e7d7e8c5e7fe00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5dd2",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "谢谢你一路陪着我这个不可靠的舰长、走{00}到这里",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b2e8b2e7b8efb6e8d2ef42e86defcce7b9e828e7b5e7c4e8c7e7b4e7d4ef3402e89000e7d7e7b9ef310000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5df1",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『平成高达路线』就到此结束了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce887e837e812ef2be8d2e9160de7c5e7d7e7cae868e895e7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5e0f",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、我们预防者的战斗、虽然已经结束{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602efcce7bbea5ae968ef6ee7b4ef28e7ff02e8b8e7efef3ae8b7e868e895000909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5e29",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……但游戏本身仍可继续、今后也请你尽{00}情享受",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7dbea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02efb9e7fee7c0e83ae7b8e8f200e88bec06e8c800000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5e4f",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "还为通关这条路线的你、准备了新的关卡{00}哦",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f7e7c1ef59e8bbe7b9e9d4e8d2e916e7b4e7b802e87ae877e7baef8ae7b4e8bbe80100e9190000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5e73",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是另与提坦斯、新吉翁交战过的……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e99be832e821e843e7c802ef8ae7d9ee88e861ef28ef36e7b40909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5e8e",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……与隆德·贝尔队的特别演习哦",
   "zh_hex": "150909e832ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e7b4e7cfe7e5ea2feab6e919000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5ea1",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特别演习』、就能与{00}他们交战哦",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efb5e8a6e7beef28ef4ee966eaaa0ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d02e7c5e7c6e83200e80ce7bbe861ef28e91900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5ec7",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请务必来挑战看看哦",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae94fe860efcfeae7ef28e7f6e7f6e919000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5ed5",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、『SD高达G世代DS』",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd020cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83ce8e7ef96ef9e0d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5ef9",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『自由对战的战火！冲过去吧、大天使号{00}！！』",
   "zh_hex": "150cefb5e8a6e7beef28e7b4ef28e8daef97e95eef36e7ebe7d002efa5e844e83fe83300ef97ef970d000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5f7a",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是主天使号舰长、娜塔尔·巴基露露中{00}佐",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6e954e844e83fe833e7d4ef3402e7eae945e7e1ef4be85be829e858e858ef4e00efba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5f8a",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "首先、请容我向你一路以来出色的指挥致{00}以敬意",
   "zh_hex": "15ef40b802e83aed2f8b9de7b887e8d2e7f3d9afe89fe7b4e8c0e949ea3200e7f3ee38ef3c000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5fac",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "多亏有你的协助、我们才得以奋战到最后",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e9eab7e7cbe7b8e7b4e8f6ea2302efcce7bbe836e80ae7f3ef46ef28e7d7e8c5e7fe00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5fce",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『对手路线』就到此结束了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce7beef66e8d2e9160de7c5e7d7e7cae868e895e7ba00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5fe4",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、我们主天使队的战斗、虽已就此结{00}束……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602efcce7bbe954e844e83fe7c9e7b4ef28e7ff02e8b8ef3ae7c5e7cae86800e895090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5ffd",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过游戏本身仍可继续、今后也请你尽情{00}享受",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef36ea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02efb9e7fee7c0e83ae7b8e8f2e88b00ec06e8c800000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6021",
   "jp_len": 43,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "自由对战今后仍可继续、此外、只要选择{00}『特别演习』……",
   "zh_hex": "15efb5e8a6e7beef28efb9e7feeab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02e7cae8f702ef32ef2ae966eaaa000ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d0909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x604c",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "便能与隆德·贝尔、预防者进行联合演习",
   "zh_hex": "15e8fae7c6e832ed16e82cef4be857e7e102ea5ae968ef6ee892efd6ef2eefc0ea2feab6000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x606a",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我相信、与他们一战、你也必定能取得胜{00}利",
   "zh_hex": "158be8b1e90f02e832e80ce7bb87ef2802e7b8e7c0e860e867e7c6e987e80ae8db00e82e0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x608f",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、『SD高达G世代DS』",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd020cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83ce8e7ef96ef9e0d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x60b3",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后也祝你武运长久",
   "zh_hex": "15efb9e7fee7c0ed97e7b8e8ece986ef34e9db000000"
  }
 ]
}
